msgctxt "paragraph"
msgid "<g id='169'>Parole is a modern simple media player based on the </g><g id='170'><g id='171'>GStreamer</g></g><g id='172'> framework and written to fit well in the </g><g id='173'><g id='174'>Xfce</g></g><g id='175'> desktop. Parole is designed with simplicity, speed and resource usage in mind. </g>"
