#: SalixStartupGuide-en.odt:2
msgctxt "paragraph"
msgid "Salix LXDE edition features the Lightweight X11 Desktop Environment, “<g id='359'>an extremely fast-performing and energy-saving desktop environment</g>”, with a clean look and feel."
msgstr "Salix LXDE edition presenta l'ambiente desktop leggero X11“<g id='359'>estremamente veloce e dai bassi comsumi energetici</g>”, con un aspetto chiaro e lineare."

